<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?>
<?xml-stylesheet type="text/xsl" href="../helpproject.xsl" ?>
<topic template="Default" version="2" xmlns:xsi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance" xsi:noNamespaceSchemaLocation="../helpproject.xsd">
  <title>3.1 &quot;Emergency Stop&quot; Switch</title>
  <keywords>
    <keyword>#MCVIEW</keyword>
    <keyword>#MECHOK</keyword>
    <keyword>#MPG</keyword>
    <keyword>#OPPANEL</keyword>
  </keywords>
  <body>
    <header>
      <para styleclass="Heading3">“紧急停止”开关</para>
    </header>
    <para styleclass="Normal" style="margin-top:8px;"><table styleclass="Default" rowcount="1" colcount="2" style="border-width:0px; border-spacing:0px; border-collapse:collapse; cell-border-width:1px; border-color:#000000; border-style:solid;">
      <tr style="vertical-align:top">
        <td style="vertical-align:middle; width:112px; border-right:none;">
          <para styleclass="" style="text-align:center; text-indent:0px; margin-top:8px; margin-right:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; line-height:1.00; background-color:transparent; white-space:normal; page-break-inside:auto; page-break-after:auto; border:none; tabstops:none;"><image src="Danger symbol no text.png" scale="16.00%" width="42" height="37" styleclass="Image Caption"></image></para>
          <para styleclass="" style="text-align:center; text-indent:0px; margin-top:3px; margin-right:0px; margin-bottom:3px; margin-left:0px; line-height:1.00; background-color:transparent; white-space:normal; page-break-inside:auto; page-break-after:auto; border:none; tabstops:none;"><text styleclass="" style="font-family:SimSun; font-size:11pt; font-weight:bold; color:#231f20;">警告</text></para>
        </td>
        <td style="vertical-align:middle; width:589px; border-left:none;">
          <list id="3" type="ul" listtype="bullet" formatstring="&#8226;" levelreset="true" legalstyle="false" startfrom="0" styleclass="" style="text-align:left; text-indent:-11px; margin-top:0px; margin-right:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:11px; line-height:1.00; background-color:transparent; white-space:normal; page-break-inside:auto; page-break-after:auto; border:none; tabstops:117px left ; font-family:Arial; font-size:11pt; color:#000000;">
            <li styleclass="" style="text-align:left; text-indent:-11px; margin-top:0px; margin-right:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:11px; line-height:1.00; background-color:transparent; white-space:normal; page-break-inside:auto; page-break-after:auto; border:none; tabstops:117px left ;"><text styleclass="" style="font-family:SimSun; font-size:11pt; font-weight:bold; color:#000000;">在执行机床操作或维护之前，确保操作人员知道所有“紧急停止”开关的位置，以便在机床异常或危险时刻立即触发此类开关。</text></li>
          </list>
        </td>
      </tr>
    </table></para>
    <para styleclass="Normal"></para>
    <para styleclass="Normal" style="text-align:justify; margin-bottom:8px;"><text style="font-size:11pt;">按下“紧急停止”开关之后，机床会呈现下述状态:</text></para>
    <list id="4" type="ul" listtype="bullet" formatstring="&#183;" format-charset="SYMBOL_CHARSET" levelreset="true" legalstyle="false" startfrom="1" styleclass="Normal" style="text-align:justify; margin-left:26px; line-height:1.30; font-family:Symbol; font-size:11pt; color:#000000;">
      <li styleclass="Normal" style="text-align:justify; margin-left:26px; line-height:1.30;"><text style="font-size:11pt;">每个轴的进给会立即停止。</text></li>
      <li styleclass="Normal" style="text-align:justify; margin-left:26px; line-height:1.30;"><text style="font-size:11pt;">如果主轴在旋转的话会立即停止。</text></li>
      <li styleclass="Normal" style="text-align:justify; margin-left:26px; line-height:1.30;"><text style="font-size:11pt;">如果主轴未夹紧的话会夹紧。</text></li>
      <li styleclass="Normal" style="text-align:justify; margin-left:26px; line-height:1.30;"><text style="font-size:11pt;">如果主轴按既定方向行进的话，该方向会被复位。</text></li>
      <li styleclass="Normal" style="text-align:justify; margin-left:26px; line-height:1.18;"><text style="font-size:11pt;">换刀或刀库正在运转时，运转会立即停止（即使在运动之中）。</text></li>
      <li styleclass="Normal" style="text-align:justify; margin-left:26px; line-height:1.30;"><text style="font-size:11pt;">操作过程中的排屑器和内部碎屑输送器会立即停止。</text></li>
      <li styleclass="Normal" style="text-align:justify; margin-left:26px; line-height:1.30;"><text style="font-size:11pt;">液压装置停止。</text></li>
      <li styleclass="Normal" style="text-align:justify; margin-left:26px; line-height:1.30;"><text style="font-size:11pt;">切削液供应停止。</text></li>
      <li styleclass="Normal" style="text-align:justify; margin-left:26px; line-height:1.30;"><text style="font-size:11pt;">加工室的扫吹气停止。</text><conditional-text type="IF" value="GRAPHITE"/></li>
    </list>
    <list id="5" type="ul" listtype="bullet" formatstring="&#183;" format-charset="SYMBOL_CHARSET" levelreset="true" legalstyle="false" startfrom="1" styleclass="Normal" style="text-align:justify; margin-left:26px; line-height:1.30; font-family:Symbol; font-size:11pt; color:#ff0000;">
      <li styleclass="Normal" style="text-align:justify; margin-left:26px; line-height:1.30;"><text style="font-size:11pt; color:#ff0000;">集尘器的抽吸动作停止（石墨规格）。</text><conditional-text type="END"/><conditional-text type="IF" value="APC"/></li>
      <li styleclass="Normal" style="text-align:justify; margin-left:26px; line-height:1.30;"><text style="font-size:11pt; color:#ff0000;">The pallet changer is stopped.</text><conditional-text type="END"/></li>
    </list>
    <list id="4" type="ul" listtype="bullet" formatstring="&#183;" format-charset="SYMBOL_CHARSET" levelreset="true" legalstyle="false" startfrom="1" styleclass="Normal" style="text-align:justify; margin-left:26px; line-height:1.30; font-family:Symbol; font-size:11pt; color:#000000;">
      <li styleclass="Normal" style="text-align:justify; margin-left:26px; line-height:1.30;"><text style="font-size:11pt;">所有通电的电磁阀被复位。</text></li>
      <li styleclass="Normal" style="text-align:justify; margin-left:26px; line-height:1.30;"><text style="font-size:11pt;">数控复位。</text></li>
    </list>
    <para styleclass="Normal" style="text-align:justify; margin-top:8px; margin-bottom:8px; line-height:1.18;"><text style="font-size:11pt;">一旦按下“紧急停止”开关，它就会被锁定在这个位置上。通过拨动方向开关或拔出开关就可以脱开门锁。然后，按下</text><text style="font-size:11pt; font-weight:bold;">[控制电源开]</text><text style="font-size:11pt;">开关取消紧急停止状态。</text></para>
    <para styleclass="Normal" style="text-align:justify; line-height:1.18;"><text style="font-size:11pt;">因按下“紧急停止”开关致使操作停止之后相关恢复程序(</text><text style="font-size:11pt; color:#0000ff;">请参阅2.1紧急停止状态的恢复第8章故障排除</text><text style="font-size:11pt;">)。</text></para>
    <para styleclass="Normal" style="margin-bottom:8px; page-break-before:always;"><text style="font-size:11pt;">于下列位置处安装有“紧急停止”开关。所有按钮的功能都相同。</text></para>
    <para styleclass="Normal" style="margin-bottom:8px;"></para>
    <para styleclass="Normal" style="text-align:center; margin-bottom:8px;"><image src="ESS_1.png" scale="90.00%" width="730" height="774" styleclass="Image Caption"></image></para>
    <para styleclass="Normal" style="text-align:center;"></para>
    <para styleclass="Normal" style="text-align:center; margin-bottom:15px;"><text styleclass="" style="font-family:SimSun; font-size:11pt; color:#000000;">图</text><text styleclass="Figure E" style="font-size:11pt;"> &lt;%HMFIGURECOUNTER1=3%&gt;.&lt;%HMFIGURECOUNTER=1%&gt; </text><text style="font-size:11pt;">“紧急停止”开关</text></para>
    <para styleclass="Normal" style="text-align:center;"><table styleclass="Default" rowcount="2" colcount="2" style="border-width:0px; border-spacing:0px; border-collapse:collapse; cell-border-width:1px; border-color:#000000; border-style:solid;">
      <tr style="vertical-align:top">
        <td style="width:45px; background-color:#dddddd;">
          <para styleclass="Normal" style="text-align:center; margin-top:3px;"><text styleclass="" style="font-family:SimSun; font-size:10pt; color:#000000; letter-scaling:105%;">序号</text></para>
        </td>
        <td style="width:444px; background-color:#dddddd;">
          <para styleclass="Normal" style="text-align:center; margin-top:3px; margin-bottom:3px;"><text styleclass="" style="font-family:SimSun; font-size:10pt; color:#000000; letter-scaling:105%;">名称</text></para>
        </td>
      </tr>
      <tr style="vertical-align:top">
        <td style="width:45px;">
          <para styleclass="Normal" style="text-align:center; margin-top:2px; margin-bottom:2px;"><text style="font-size:10pt;">1</text></para>
        </td>
        <td style="width:444px;">
          <para styleclass="Normal" style="text-align:justify; margin-top:2px; margin-bottom:2px; margin-left:4px;"><text style="font-size:10pt;">“紧急停止”开关</text></para>
        </td>
      </tr>
    </table></para>
    <para styleclass="Normal" style="text-align:center;"><conditional-text type="IF" value="OPTION"/></para>
    <para styleclass="Normal" style="text-align:center; margin-top:8px; margin-bottom:8px;"><image src="ESS_2.png" scale="65.00%" width="462" height="443" styleclass="Image Caption"></image></para>
    <para styleclass="Normal" style="text-align:center; margin-bottom:10px;"><text styleclass="" style="font-family:SimSun; font-size:11pt; color:#000000;">图</text><text styleclass="Figure E" style="font-size:11pt;"> &lt;%HMFIGURECOUNTER1=3%&gt;.&lt;%HMFIGURECOUNTER%&gt; </text><text style="font-size:11pt;">“紧急停止”开关</text></para>
    <para styleclass="Normal" style="text-align:center; margin-top:8px;"><table styleclass="Default" rowcount="2" colcount="2" style="border-width:0px; border-spacing:0px; border-collapse:collapse; cell-border-width:1px; border-color:#000000; border-style:solid;">
      <tr style="vertical-align:top">
        <td style="width:45px; background-color:#dddddd;">
          <para styleclass="Normal" style="text-align:center; margin-top:3px;"><text styleclass="" style="font-family:SimSun; font-size:10pt; color:#000000; letter-scaling:105%;">序号</text></para>
        </td>
        <td style="width:444px; background-color:#dddddd;">
          <para styleclass="Normal" style="text-align:center; margin-top:3px; margin-bottom:3px;"><text styleclass="" style="font-family:SimSun; font-size:10pt; color:#000000; letter-scaling:105%;">名称</text></para>
        </td>
      </tr>
      <tr style="vertical-align:top">
        <td style="width:45px;">
          <para styleclass="Normal" style="text-align:center; margin-top:2px; margin-bottom:2px;"><text style="font-size:10pt;">1</text></para>
        </td>
        <td style="width:444px;">
          <para styleclass="Normal" style="text-align:justify; margin-top:2px; margin-bottom:2px; margin-left:4px;"><text style="font-size:10pt;">“紧急停止”开关</text></para>
        </td>
      </tr>
    </table></para>
    <para styleclass="Normal" style="text-align:center;"><conditional-text type="END"/></para>
    <para styleclass="Normal" style="text-align:center; page-break-before:always;"></para>
  </body>
</topic>
